<item>
            <title>[SOLR-8564] ZK data directory being set incorrectly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8564</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When you start solr using the embedded zookeeper the data directory is not being set correctly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead of the zookeeper data directory being server/solr/zoo_data the data directory becomes server/solrzoo_data . This seems to happen only from 5.4 onwards.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;~/solr-5.4.0 $ ./bin/solr start -s server/solr -c 
~/solr-5.4.0 $ ls server/
README.txt	contexts	etc		lib		logs		modules		resources	scripts		solr		solr-webapp	solrzoo_data	start.jar
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch coming up&lt;/p&gt;</description>
