                            <comment id="15106609" author="varunthacker" created="Tue, 19 Jan 2016 11:24:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It shouldn&apos;t right? It&apos;s only the directory where the zookeeper data is present thats different.&lt;/p&gt;

